Relegation playoff [Dec 21]
Palmeiras         0-1  Fluminense
  [Palmeiras walks over at minute 70' (30' of second half) after a
   penalty kick was awarded to Fluminense. Result stood.]

Palmeiras are relegated to 1931 Série B and Fluminense are promoted to 1931 Série A.


*** PALESTRA ITÁLIA are the Minas Gerais unbeaten champions of 1930 ***

** Topscorer: Ninão (Palestra Itália) 18 goals **

